Dense matrices over $\Z/n\Z$ for $n$ small.

AUTHORS:
    -- William Stein
    -- Robert Bradshaw

This is a compiled implementation of dense matrices over $\Z/n\Z$
for $n$ small.

EXAMPLES:
    sage: a = matrix(Integers(37),3,range(9),sparse=False); a
    [0 1 2]
    [3 4 5]
    [6 7 8]
